text: Mister International Korea () is a male beauty pageant. It is held every year, to sselect South Korea's representatives to the Mister International, Mister Global, Mister Supranational and Man of the World pageant. . == History == Previously, the Korean representatives were selected through an online announcement or an unofficial public contest, but in 2013, the tournament was officially held and Kim Jae Hyuk took the first win. The first competition was held in 2013. == References == == Other websites == * Category:Beauty pageants
